Module com.project.schedule_app
Package Tableviews

Class Appointments

java.lang.Object
Tableviews.AppointmentsTableview
public class Appointments extends Object
Appointments stores a modified version of DBAppointments, specifically meant to be displayed in TableViews. It's attributes are stored as ObservableValue Objects.
